Global Infectious Diseases Molecular Diagnostics Kit Market Insights
Infectious Diseases Molecular Diagnostics Kit Market size was valued at USD 5.3 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 9.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.9% from 2024 to 2030.

Infectious Diseases Molecular Diagnostics Kit Market Overview
The global market for Infectious Diseases Molecular Diagnostics Kits is witnessing significant growth, driven by the increasing demand for precise and rapid diagnostic tools in the healthcare sector. The market size was valued at USD 6.15 billion in 2024 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 8.6% from 2024 to 2032. Advancements in molecular diagnostic technologies and increasing prevalence of infectious diseases are expected to propel market expansion. This growth is further fueled by the rising demand for point-of-care testing and the growing focus on personalized healthcare solutions.

